title: Corby Town defender Jason Lee celebrated his side’s winner by taking a swig of a fans pint against Mickleover Sports in the Evo-Stik Northern Premier League
text:
EFL Bottoms up Corby Town defender Jason Lee celebrated his side’s winner by taking a swig of a fans pint against Mickleover Sports in the Evo-Stik Northern Premier League 
The second half strike lifted the Steelmen out of the relegation zone and they have now won four league matches in a row by jake lambourne
